Narrator

Golden knives were handed to all of us.

Player_Romus

"Thank you for attending."

Sal Ignacius

"We have so much we can do together. I can help you, as I helped your father."

Sal Ignacius

"Such believers can be... utilized to aid the goals of the crown. I pray you will make the right choice."

Angelica Sazon

"Before my exile, I was one of the most educated noblewomen in Brenas. On Caleqabiz, I spent much of my time reading about the principles of governance."

Angelica Sazon

"That is what I can offer to you and to the crown. Nothing more, nothing less."

Rico Toras

"You know very well what I am capable of, cousin."

Taddeus Azaro

"All my life I have fought for this country. I bled for it. I went through hell for it."

Taddeus Azaro

"War will come to Rizia someday, sire. And to protect the interests of my proud kingdom, I am ready to die a thousand deaths."

Taddeus Azaro

"My daughter is ready to step aside. She has another role to play now."

Titus Gordion

"I protected you and your father for many years as part of the Golden Guard and hopefully I will do so for many more."

Titus Gordion

"Trust in me and the Golden Guard, and security will never be a worry in Rizia again."

Daria de Rava

"During my tenure at the House of Delegates, I made many successful career moves and also ended others' careers."

Russello Montoro

"That's right. I want this job so much I'm willing to go through *all* the formalities. I even bought a new tie."

Russello Montoro

"I've already helped make Rizia money. Think about how much more I could do as treasurer."

Russello Montoro

"Just look at how much gold we're hauling out of the ground right now. All thanks to me."

Russello Montoro

"Not to mention that if you're looking to get closer to ATO... well, I can help you with that. If you know what I mean."

Vina Toras

"Father. I know you still see me as your little girl. Maybe you don't think that I am ready."

Vina Toras

"Laurento has been like a grandfather to me, but he's past his prime and you know it. It's time for the younger generation to represent Rizia on the global stage."

Vina Toras

"As for me... well, you know better than anybody that work is all I have."

Vina Toras

"We have had our differences. But please. Grant me this."

Narrator

The ritual had finally ended.

Narrator

I looked at the bright red, sizzling molten gold until my eyes began to water.

PlayLoopedMusic("R_Continuation", "R_Continuation_Loop");
